{"about_the_game":"Do you have what it takes to overcome the challenges of Vibrant Valley? <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPhaser presents a unique take on the 2D-platformer formula by allowing you, the player, to take control of each level. By learning the power of color-switching, you will be able to phase in and out challenging obstacles from your path, find new and creative ways to victory, and avoid otherwise certain death. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this world, you will face both tests of speed and cunning. Some levels demand a snappy reaction time while others require careful thought and consideration. Nothing is as simple as it may seem.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nContinue striving to do better with achievements and trackable stats. Best time and lowest deaths are recorded for every level. Keep mastering each level for endless replayability. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nHaving trouble on a level? Enter practice mode and play any level for a more casual way to hone your skills.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy hours of unique and exciting platforming gameplay and see if you have the skill to be a phaser.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"World One Bronze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1320400/b774c4447e1fb7d3c5c565352f5dc10d88e5c1b4.jpg"},{"name":"World One Silver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1320400/b91331fa056c80344896841d2a5c8d92dc94cec2.jpg"},{"name":"World One Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1320400/271bbe26556bb6a452d23556781aee5a6b636661.jpg"},{"name":"World One Diamond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1320400/3e411bf7c9de7447dc824597e71ebecdaef18c76.jpg"},{"name":"World Two Bronze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1320400/81034d6ef4f105af40685393f90fcabaab8f78f5.jpg"},{"name":"World Two Silver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/p